<head>COAL</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">煤炭</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>BLACK SUBSTANCE PRODUCED USING TIMBER, AND USED FOR BURNING.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The standard word for charcoal is tàn 炭.</p>
<p>Current post-Buddhist words for coal were 石煤，石墨，石炭. Méi tàn 煤炭 is first attested in Sòng times.</p>
        </div>
